🎨 Color Picker

This project is a simple interactive Color Picker built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

✨ Features

Four color buttons with predefined Hex codes.

Clicking a button changes the background color of the page.

The selected Hex code is displayed dynamically on the screen.

The button text and displayed Hex code always match the chosen color.

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML – Structure of the page

CSS / Bootstrap – Styling and layout

JavaScript – Functionality to switch colors

📌 How it Works

Click on any color button.

The background color of the container changes to that color.

The selected Hex code updates in the display.
